Given this, if the U.S. is serious about AGI, then the true Manhattan Proje=
ct =E2=80=94 doing something that will be very expensive and not necessaril=
y economically rational =E2=80=94 is filling in the middle of the sandwich.=
 Saving Intel, in other words.

